item.title: Need server help!
item.dc:creator: @Tylerholmes Tylerholmes
item.description:
@Tylerholmes wrote:

1f unit pker:

I am having trouble putting my server online? how do I do it? I’m confused… do I have to do something special?

Okay, i will help you.

First off, Portforward.
If you dont know how, go to http://www.portforward.com/
and look for the guide.

After you read the guide, do what it says.

Now follow these steps.

1.)Set up no-ip (So easy a cave man/woman can do it)
2.)Change every address with localhost to the no-ip IP
3.)save,compile,start,run

Now your ready to go!

-Tyler
Fatality Owner
